entries.title: Surfer's Paradise lifeguard rescues woman on New Year's Eve after she was swept out to sea

entries.title: Ex-government terrorism tsar advises partner of blacklisted Chinese firm working on nuclear weapons

entries.title: Parents demand principal of US' top public school be fired after she withheld prestigious awards
